dataIdInfo.idAbs:
Polygons of Myanmar State, Region and Union territory boundaries (Admin1) with Sub-regions, based on the latest MIMU Pcode version 9.4 and information provided by field offices and government departments. Place names from General Administration Department (GAD), are available in Myanmar Unicode. Transliteration in roman script by MIMU.

This dataset was mainly digitized at 1:250,000 scale. Place names are in line with the general cartographic practice to reflect the names of such places as designated by the host governments. The information contained on this product is provided “as is”, for reference purposes only, based on current available information. The United Nations and the MIMU specifically do not make any warranties or representations as to the accuracy or completeness of such information nor does it imply official endorsement or acceptance by the United Nations. Please share any errors or omissions via maps@themimu.info.

Consts.useLimit: This product has been prepared for operational purposes only, to support humanitarian and development activities in Myanmar. Copyright ©2020 Myanmar Information Management Unit. For more information see http://themimu.info/mimu-terms-conditions.

dataIdInfo.idCredit: Place Names from General Administration Department (GAD). Transliteration by MIMU. Coordinates by MIMU. Boundaries by MIMU.

dataLineage.statement:
Layer was downloaded by ITOS from HDX. It was then analyzed by ITOS for errors. Those errors were kept as-is and then the layer was sent back to UNOCHA as a feature class within a file geodatabase.
The following was found by ITOS: 1. 3 gap errors were found. 2. 15 nesting errors exist among layers.
